  m_EditorHideFlags: 0
  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: 8f286a325ac54b1ca29fc115bc9912c0, type: 3}
  m_Name: EP3LobbyIntroSequence
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  sequenceId: EP3_LOBBY_INTRO
  shots:
  - dialogueId: EP3_001
    speakerType: Narration
    speakerName: 
    subtitleText: 낯선 정적이 작업실 안에 가라앉아 있었다.
    showSpeakerName: 0
    cameraPosition: {x: 3.25, y: 2.3, z: -27.8}
    lookAtPosition: {x: 3.35, y: 1.4, z: -20.5}
    moveDuration: 1.8
    holdDuration: 1.5
    fieldOfView: 50
  - dialogueId: EP3_002
    speakerType: Narration
    speakerName: 
    subtitleText: 누군가 방금 전까지 머물렀던 것처럼, 악기와 흔적들만이 자리를 지키고 있었다.
    showSpeakerName: 0
    cameraPosition: {x: 6.2, y: 2.35, z: -18.7}
    lookAtPosition: {x: 0.8, y: 1.2, z: -12.2}
    moveDuration: 2.3
    holdDuration: 1.6
    fieldOfView: 48
  - dialogueId: EP3_003
    speakerType: Narration
    speakerName: 
    subtitleText: 완성되지 못한 멜로디가 이 공간 어딘가에 남아 있는 듯했다.
    showSpeakerName: 0
    cameraPosition: {x: 2.2, y: 4.85, z: -11.2}
    lookAtPosition: {x: 0.9, y: 1.35, z: -10.7}
    moveDuration: 2.4
    holdDuration: 1.7
    fieldOfView: 56
  - dialogueId: EP3_004
    speakerType: Narration
    speakerName: 
    subtitleText: 벽에 남겨진 심볼과 악기들은, 멈춰버린 기억의 조각처럼 보였다.
    showSpeakerName: 0
    cameraPosition: {x: 4.7, y: 2.5, z: -10}
    lookAtPosition: {x: 2.8, y: 1.3, z: -17}
    moveDuration: 2
    holdDuration: 1.7
    fieldOfView: 45
  - dialogueId: EP3_005
    speakerType: Monologue
    speakerName: 
    subtitleText: 이곳에서, 잊힌 노래의 첫 단서를 찾아야 한다.
    showSpeakerName: 0
    cameraPosition: {x: 3.4, y: 2.25, z: -24.6}
    lookAtPosition: {x: 3.3, y: 1.2, z: -34.3}
    moveDuration: 2.4
    holdDuration: 2
    fieldOfView: 43
